title: Forever Knight Complete Soundtrack (2 CD's)
description:
The entire released soundtracks to the 90&#039;s TV show "Forever Knight" with Geraint Wyn Davies and Nigel Bennett.  Two CD&#039;s, each with over twenty tracks!  

And if you don&#039;t care about the score, that&#039;s fine, because those songs you liked in the background of the scenes in the Raven nightclub are on here too!

It took me a while to find these, and I&#039;m glad to have them, so I hope you enjoy them as much as I do.
